 ('492', '492', 'en_us', 'Report a Problem', 'Report flooding, landslides, blocked roadways, overflowing storm drains, sewers and other debris to the City of Oakland.', '<p><strong>Downed Power line? Smell gas?</strong>&nbsp;Leave the area immediately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call 9-1-1 or PG&E at (800) 743-5000.</p><br><br>Power outage?&nbsp;Report and see maps of outages&nbsp;online by PG&E.&nbsp;Visit:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://m.pge.com/#outages\">http://m.pge.com/#outages</a><p><br></p>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Issues with water?&nbsp;</strong>(e.g., no water service, broken hydrants, broken water main pipes) Call&nbsp;East Bay Municipal Utility District&nbsp;at&nbsp;(866) 403-2683.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Still need help?Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:opwcallcenter@oaklandnet.com\">opwcallcenter@oaklandnet.com</a><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, 'information', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-01-12 22:56:52', '2016-03-01 18:36:07', '17361840-e0a5-4381-aacb-ea0db45f9182'),
