 ('1642', '1892', 'en_us', 'Schedule an Inspection with the Police Department', '', '<p>You will need to schedule inspections with the Oakland Police Department if your business:</p><ul><li>involves&nbsp;cannabis, alcohol, or cabaret</li><li>hosts&nbsp;special events such as&nbsp;concerts</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-02-17 01:57:30', '2016-03-01 18:36:14', '4a8c3afc-cd52-4f63-aa27-90161c4bb5a8'),
