 ('2042', '2432', 'en_us', 'Fiscal Year 2015-2017 Budget for the City of Oakland', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '[]', NULL, 'info', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'hide', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>On June 30, the Oakland City Council approved a $2.4 billion two-year budget for fiscal years 2015-2017. The budget closes an estimated $18 million annual funding gap without making any cuts to City services or staffing levels.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-01 00:28:13', '2016-03-02 21:11:10', 'caf557f9-3288-439c-9f39-06ee22a23f24'),
