ess name with the Alameda County Clerk-Recorder\'s Office.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.acgov.org\\/auditor\\/clerk\\/filefbn1.htm\\\">More details from Alameda County Clerk-Recorder\'s Office<\\/a><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Retail\\/Wholesale Sales<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you will be selling retail or wholesale items which require collection of state sales taxes, you need a Sellers Permit.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.boe.ca.gov\\/\\\">More details from California State Board of Equalization<\\/a><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Food Establishments<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you will be serving and selling food, you must obtain a health permit before applying for your Business Tax Certificate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.acgov.org\\/aceh\\/\\\">More details from Alameda County Environmental Health<\\/a><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Alcoholic Beverage Sales<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>If you intend to sell alcoholic beverages, you must have an Alcoholic Beverage License.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.abc.ca.gov\\/\\\">More details from California state Alcoholic Beverage Control<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"Learn more about permits that are required by common business types\"}}', '2016-01-27 23:12:43', '2016-01-27 23:12:43', '8ff06e31-6e65-409b-b335-1a170956692f'),
