 ('3032', '112', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Renew Your Residential Parking Permit\",\"slug\":\"renew-your-residential-parking-permit\",\"postDate\":1450476960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"52\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>You can renew your permit online if you received a letter that says you are eligible for online renewal.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Renew your permit online\",\"linkUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/pci.etimspayments.com\\/pbw\\/include\\/oakland\\/rppinput.jsp\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"In Person or by Mail\",\"address\":\"<p>Attn: Residential Parking Permits<br><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:30:16', '2016-02-10 00:30:16', '05fa917a-5616-409a-bf3c-d66945835aee'),
 ('3042', '872', '3', '1', 'en_us', '8', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain a Zoning Clearance Permit\",\"slug\":\"obtain-a-zoning-permit\",\"postDate\":1453931700,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>If you plan to operate a business in Oakland (including a home office), you will need to obtain a zoning permit called a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>. You do not need a&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Clearance<\\/strong>&nbsp;if your business is located outside of Oakland or if your business activity is a rental property operator. The Zoning Clearance is granted if your business is allowed in the proposed location. In some instances, ahead of obtaining a Zoning Clearance, a proposed business activity must also go through a special&nbsp;<strong>Conditional Use Permit&nbsp;<\\/strong>process to determine whether the activity will be allowed.&nbsp;<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Zoning Clearance is a one-time permit that is good as long as the nature of your business remains the same and in the same location. You will need this zoning permit before applying for your business tax certificate.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>You may obtain additional information about zoning permits and regulations via the&nbsp;<strong>Zoning Hotline<\\/strong>&nbsp;(telephone), the&nbsp;<strong>Online Zoning Request Form<\\/strong>&nbsp;or by visiting the&nbsp;<strong>Permit Counter. Zoning Clearances<\\/strong>&nbsp;and other zoning permit applications are available online, but must be submitted and paid for in person at the Permit Counter.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Download the application\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/oakca1\\/groups\\/ceda\\/documents\\/agenda\\/oak040732.pdf\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"phoneNumber\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"number\":\"1 (510) 238-3911\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Turning In Your Application\",\"address\":\"<p>Permit Counter<br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Room 2114<br>Oakland, CA 94612<span><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"A zoning clearance permit is required if you plan to operate your business in Oakland\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:32:49', '2016-02-10 00:32:49', 'f259eac8-4d29-472c-b6bc-82099bef36bd'),
 ('3052', '952', '3', '1', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Obtain Your Business Tax Certificate\",\"slug\":\"obtain-your-business-license\",\"postDate\":1453934640,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"922\",\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Before you start, you will need your <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/obtain-a-zoning-permit#entry:872:url\\\">Zoning Clearance<\\/a> and <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/register-your-business-name#entry:942:url\\\">Fictitious Business Name<\\/a> applications approved.&nbsp;For more detail on&nbsp;exceptions on who needs a business tax certificate, click&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/#entry:2:url\\\"><\\/a><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/beta.oaklandca.gov\\/services\\/businesses\\/start-your-business\\/register-your-business\\/confirm-if-you-need-to-register-your-business#entry:1082:url\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Cost<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The $88&nbsp;registration fee must be paid and filed within 30 days of starting your business.&nbsp; If you file your registration later than 30 days after you start your business, you will need to pay a small penalty plus interest for each month beyond the 30 days.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Application Process<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The New Business&nbsp;Application is available online&nbsp;and at our offices.&nbsp;You can pay by&nbsp;cash, check, cashier\'s check, money order,&nbsp;credit cards (Mastercard, Visa, & Discover),&nbsp;and ATM debit cards.&nbsp;However, if paying with an&nbsp;ATM&nbsp;debit card you must come into the office.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The application can&nbsp;be returned by fax (with a&nbsp;credit card), via mail or in person. If submitting by fax, you may pay by phone by&nbsp;provide the social security number or federal tax identification number on record.&nbsp;You will get a paper certificate from the business tax office approximately two weeks after you pay your fee.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Business Tax Office Hours<\\/h3><p>Monday,&nbsp;Tuesday, Thursday, Friday&nbsp;8&nbsp;a.m.&nbsp;\\u2013&nbsp;4:00 p.m<br>Wednesday, 9:30 a.m. \\u2013 4:00 p.m<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Renewal<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Business taxes must be paid annually, on or before March 1st of each year. It is your responsibility to renew your certificate on time and\\/or to notify the Business Tax Office if you have not received your annual renewal declaration(s).<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<hr>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Non-Profit Registation<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>All non-profit organizations located or doing business in the City of Oakland are required to register with the city. To register as a non-profit, you must first have your 501(c)(3) from the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.irs.gov\\/Charities-&-Non-Profits\\\">IRS<\\/a>, the Letter of Exemption from the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.boe.ca.gov\\/info\\/VirtualSeminars\\/nonprofit_resources.html\\\">California State Franchise Board<\\/a>, a copy of your Articles of Incorporation, and, if you have a location in the City of Oakland, a zoning clearance for your business location (please contact the&nbsp;<u><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Government\\/o\\/PBN\\/OurOrganization\\/PlanningZoning\\/o\\/Zoning\\/index.htm\\\">Zoning Division<\\/a><\\/u>&nbsp;to obtain zoning clearance).&nbsp;Once you have obtained the above documents you must complete a&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.oaklandnet.com\\/government\\/fwawebsite\\/revenue\\/revenue_newbiaapp.htm\\\">Business Registration Application<\\/a>&nbsp;and provide the City with copies of your 501(c)(3), Letter of Exemption, and Articles of Incorporation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>More Info<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Get the&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.oaklandnet.com\\/government\\/fwawebsite\\/revenue\\/revenue_biztax.htm\\\">business application (PDF), business tax classification and rate table, additional&nbsp;information, and FAQs<\\/a>&nbsp;on the City\'s Finance and Management Agency website.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Businesses located in or operating in Oakland need to pay an annual business tax on or before March 1 of each year.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/oaklandbusinesscenter.com\\/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=37&Itemid=50\\\">See more details on the annual business tax here.<\\/a><br>&nbsp;<br><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/oaklandbusinesscenter.com\\/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=102&Itemid=85\\\">Visit the BAC or request help from the BAC online<\\/a>&nbsp;if you have additional questions or need more information.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<table><tbody><tr><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table>\",\"312\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"linkTitle\":\"Download the application form\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/w\\/OAK046735\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"In Person or By Mail\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Business Tax Office<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 1320<br>Oakland, CA 94612<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"5\":\"\",\"92\":\"\",\"3\":\"\",\"4\":\"To conduct any business in Oakland you must first obtain a Business Tax Certificate and pay an annual business tax\"}}', '2016-02-10 00:36:40', '2016-02-10 00:36:40', '0c553d0e-daf5-4f77-96fb-52a40b416168'),
