sdays, Thursdays and Fridays from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<br>Wednesdays from 9:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m.<\\/p>\",\"312\":{\"1482\":{\"type\":\"onlineLink\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"onlineTitle\":\"Get the Form\",\"linkTitle\":\"Download the permit application\",\"linkUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/www2.oaklandnet.com\\/Parking\\/OAK046014\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"1\"}},\"1492\":{\"type\":\"physicalAddress\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"physicalAddressTitle\":\"Submit Your Application to:\",\"address\":\"<p><strong>Parking Citation Assistance Center<\\/strong><br>250 Frank H. Ogawa Plaza, Suite 6300<br>Oakland, CA 94612 Phone: (800) 500-6484<\\/p>\",\"primaryCallToAction\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-02-10 22:01:40', '2016-02-10 22:01:40', 'a516acf3-e267-4b65-925a-61d421ead5ef'),
