is projected to enhance Oakland\\u2019s revenue base significantly starting FY 2018-19.<\\/p>\",\"822\":{\"date\":\"3\\/2\\/2016\"},\"802\":[\"19\"],\"792\":[\"2432\"],\"812\":[\"2172\"],\"782\":[\"2524\"],\"772\":\"The purpose of the Forecast is to help make informed budgetary and operational decisions.\"}}', '2016-03-02 21:23:12', '2016-03-02 21:23:12', '61be52b7-9790-4617-b6c5-c97febfe8577'),
 ('4398', '2527', '92', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Budget Advisory Committee\'s Report on Proposed FY2015-2017 Budget Proposal\",\"slug\":\"budget-advisory-committees-report-on-proposed-fy2015-2017-budget-proposal\",\"postDate\":1456954104,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>The purpose of this memorandum is to transmit to the full City Council, Mayor, and public, the Budget Advisory Committee\\u2019s (BAC) Report on the Mayor\\u2019s Proposed FY 2015-17 Budget. The Report is submitted in accordance with the City\\u2019s Consolidated Fiscal Policy (13279 C.M.S.); and was unanimously approved at the BAC\\u2019s May 26th special meeting.<\\/p>\",\"822\":{\"date\":\"3\\/2\\/2016\"},\"802\":\"\",\"792\":[\"2432\"],\"812\":\"\",\"782\":[\"2526\"],\"772\":\"In accordance with the Consolidated Fiscal Policy the Budget Advisory Committee submits to the City Council this response to the Mayor\\u2019s proposed FY 2015-17 budget.\"}}', '2016-03-02 21:28:24', '2016-03-02 21:28:24', '28d775ba-0267-4a1c-8294-6b61e60f8d14');
