 ('212', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' thank you for your interest in working for the city of oakland for current city of oakland or port of oakland employees click here to view openings for port of oakland jobs click here to see available openings how to get started first time applicants search for jobs that fit your skills and interests save your search by setting up a job alert in a job interest card this will send you emails when new jobs open that fit your search criteria click the apply link of a job you are interested in create an account select a username and password click the build job application link to start your application save your application as you complete sections the neogov system will save your information every 15 minutes you can save and use your application to apply for other job openings online applications are stored on a secure site only authorized employees and hiring authorities have access to the information submitted tips for completing your application review the supplemental questions if any are included you may want to complete supplemental questions outside of the neogov system other recommendations include gather information about your education and work experience provide specific information in your answers such as dates locations data and references write responses in a word processing program such as microsoft word copy and paste these responses into the neogov system complete and submit your application before the closing date for consideration '),
