 ('232', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' if you believe your vehicle has been towed please call a b vehicle processing at 510 635 3211 or visit http www abimpound com towed html to confirm what to know a vehicle can be towed in oakland for any of the following reasons a boot is placed on the vehicle and payment for the boot fee and parking tickets have not been received a vehicle registration plate tag has been expired for more than six 6 months a vehicle has more than $2 500 in unpaid parking tickets a vehicle has five 5 or more unpaid tickets in the state of california how to get your vehicle released pay all of your unpaid parking tickets in oakland payment plans are not available for towed vehicles visit or call the parking citation assistance center to make payments pay fees for towing and storage directly to the tow company you may need to pay unpaid tickets from all other cities in california to have your vehicle released for more information locationhours parking citation assistance center 250 frank h ogawa plaza suite 6300 oakland ca 94612 phone 800 500 6484 mondays tuesdays thursdays and fridays from 9 a m to 4 30 p m wednesdays from 9 30 a m to 4 30 p m only the registered owner of the towed vehicle can contest one or more of the unpaid tickets please visit the parking citation assistance center at 250 frank h ogawa plaza suite 6300 or call the center at 510 238 4484 '),
