 ('1032', 'field', '1', 'en_us', ' getting certified alameda county green business program the alameda county green business program offers certification for businesses that can demonstrate that they practice resource conservation water and energy and pollution prevention toxics reduction in addition to recognizing businesses for their green practices certified green businesses can use the highly recognizable logo on their advertising and are able to network with other green businesses green business information application green america formerly co op america green america s mission is to harness economic powerthe strength of consumers businesses and the marketplaceto create a socially just and environmentally sustainable society green america helps consumers find socially and environmentally responsible businesses click here to learn more and join green america resources for greening your business business recycling and waste reduction in oakland check the stopwaste org website for comprehensive information on recycling composting reuse and waste reduction stopwaste org east bay energy watch pg e the cities of oakland and berkeley the counties of alameda and contra costa are working together on the east bay energy watch ebew bew promotes reduced energy use and energy savings targets by providing energy efficiency information and direct installation of energy efficient equipment to eligible pg e customers including lighting refrigeration building heating and cooling and other energy systems used by businesses www pge com ebep city of oakland green business projects the city has a department dedicated to green business projects and resources for the latest resources contact the business assistance center classes see a list of organizations that provide green business classes promoting and networking with other green businesses sustainable business alliance based in berkeley the sustainable business alliance is a membership organization for bay area companies committ